        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known sinonasal masses or nasal polyposis

          -  Unable to complete VAS surveys

          -  Significant septal deviation

          -  Unable to tolerate in-office flexible nasopharyngoscopy

          -  Patients who refuse consent
